product.title: Astronaut Fishing Star on Glowing Moon Humidifier Diffuser Night Light
product.body_html:
• Description
  • Shipping

  • Fill your heart with warmth

    This unique astronaut has four awesome functions: not only is it an ornament for your room, but it is also a diffuser/humidifier, aromatherapy, and night light. creating a romantic atmosphere. Featuring an astronaut sitting on the moon whilst fishing for a shooting star placed on a wooden rack.

    🎥 Video is available in the product gallery above

    Change between three different brightness levels which can be adjusted freely with the button at the top of the moon to create a romantic atmosphere. Made with a touch switch design to adjust the lighting and turn on the diffuser.

    Lift the lid from the moon and pour water into the moon and add any aromatic oils. The night light is powered via a cable (included) and is connected to the top of the moon.

    Measures: 13 x 28cm

    A night light is a must-have for many households

    This astronaut night light will light up any room, from the living room to the bedroom, or even next to your computer whenever you want to work in the dark. It is simple and unique - an awesome gift for a family or friend who loves space.

    Features

    🌚 High-quality resin and wood
    🌚 Promotes relaxation with natural soft light
    🌚 Easy-to-use tap sensor function
    🌚 Power with the cable provided
    🌚 Built-in diffuser

  • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, Spain, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.


    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: 5-20 Business days
